---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="About PPC Tool Bench – Free Tools for Google Ads Marketers"
  description="Learn about PPC Tool Bench, a free platform providing practical tools for Google Ads, campaign tracking, and ad copy optimization."
  currentPath="/about"
>
  <main class="card">
    <h1>About PPC Toolbench</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      PPC Toolbench is a practical tools site focused on Google Ads, campaign tracking,
      and ad workflow support.
    </p>

    <p>
      We built PPC Toolbench to offer simple, useful utilities for marketers,
      affiliate publishers, and campaign managers who want to work faster without
      dealing with bloated software or unnecessary complexity.
    </p>

    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <p>
      Our goal is to create focused tools that solve small but important workflow tasks,
      such as building clean UTM links, checking ad character limits, and validating
      campaign naming before launch.
    </p>

    <h2>What we believe</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Useful tools should be fast and easy to access.</li>
      <li>Core workflows should not require sign-up barriers.</li>
      <li>Clean naming and clear tracking improve campaign performance analysis.</li>
      <li>Simple products are often more helpful than complicated dashboards.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Who this site is for</h2>
    <p>
      PPC Toolbench is designed for people who run or support paid campaigns,
      affiliate promotions, email campaigns, and other marketing activities where
      accurate tracking and fast execution matter.
    </p>

    <h2>Our approach</h2>
    <p>
      We aim to publish tools that are lightweight, straightforward, and genuinely useful
      in everyday campaign work. We prefer practical interfaces, transparent guidance,
      and clear documentation over feature overload.
    </p>
  </main>
</MainLayout>